metadata.name: Mine Token GPU Collection Gen 1 #1
metadata.description: The Official Mine Token's GPU Collection Gen 1 consists of 200 unique 1 of 1 NFTs that make up the first generation of hardware NFTs released by the project.  Your collectable Gen NFT can be combined with future Mine Token NFT projects to complete a full mining rig for display in the metaverse.  It also acts as your access key to our private Discord for Mine Token NFT holders that grant members-only benefits. You will receive the the Discord Link upon purchase.
